msgid "# DeepSeek-V3.2"
msgstr "# DeepSeek-V3.2"

msgid "## Introduction"
msgstr "## 简介"

msgid ""
"DeepSeek-V3.2 is a sparse attention model. The main architecture is similar "
"to DeepSeek-V3.1, but with a sparse attention mechanism, which is designed "
"to explore and validate optimizations for training and inference efficiency "
"in long-context scenarios."
msgstr ""
"DeepSeek-V3.2 是一种稀疏注意力模型。其主要架构与 DeepSeek-V3.1 "
"类似，但引入了稀疏注意力机制，旨在探索和验证长上下文场景下训练与推理效率的优化方案。"

msgid ""
"This document will show the main verification steps of the model, including "
"supported features, feature configuration, environment preparation, single-"
"node and multi-node deployment, accuracy and performance evaluation."
msgstr "本文档将展示该模型的主要验证步骤，包括支持的特性、特性配置、环境准备、单节点与多节点部署、精度及性能评估。"

msgid "## Supported Features"
msgstr "## 支持的特性"

msgid ""
"Refer to [supported "
"features](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md) to get the "
"model's supported feature matrix."
msgstr ""
"请参考[支持的特性](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md)获取该模型支持的特性矩阵。"

msgid ""
"Refer to [feature guide](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md) to get the"
" feature's configuration."
msgstr "请参考[特性指南](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md)获取特性的配置方法。"

msgid "## Environment Preparation"
msgstr "## 环境准备"

msgid "### Model Weight"
msgstr "### 模型权重"

msgid ""
"- `DeepSeek-V3.2-Exp-W8A8` (Quantized version): requires **1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) node** or **2 Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 8) nodes**. [Download model weight](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/vllm-ascend/DeepSeek-V3.2-Exp-W8A8)\n"
"- `DeepSeek-V3.2-w8a8` (Quantized version): requires **1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) node** or **2 Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 8) nodes**. [Download model weight](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/vllm-ascend/DeepSeek-V3.2-W8A8/)"
msgstr ""
"- `DeepSeek-V3.2-Exp-W8A8`（量化版本）：需要 **1 个 Atlas 800 A3（64G × 16）节点** 或 **2 个 Atlas 800 A2（64G × 8）节点**。[下载模型权重](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/vllm-ascend/DeepSeek-V3.2-Exp-W8A8)\n"
"- `DeepSeek-V3.2-w8a8`（量化版本）：需要 **1 个 Atlas 800 A3（64G × 16）节点** 或 **2 个 Atlas 800 A2（64G × 8）节点**。[下载模型权重](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/vllm-ascend/DeepSeek-V3.2-W8A8/)"

msgid ""
"It is recommended to download the model weight to the shared directory of "
"multiple nodes, such as `/root/.cache/`."
msgstr "建议将模型权重下载到多节点的共享目录中，例如 `/root/.cache/`。"

msgid "### Verify Multi-node Communication(Optional)"
msgstr "### 验证多节点通信（可选）"

msgid ""
"If you want to deploy multi-node environment, you need to verify multi-node "
"communication according to [verify multi-node communication "
"environment](../../installation.md#verify-multi-node-communication)."
msgstr ""
"如需部署多节点环境，需按照[验证多节点通信环境](../../installation.md#verify-multi-node-"
"communication)中的说明验证多节点通信。"

msgid "### Installation"
msgstr "### 安装"

msgid "You can use our official docker image to run `DeepSeek-V3.2` directly."
msgstr "您可以直接使用官方 Docker 镜像运行 `DeepSeek-V3.2`。"

msgid ""
"In addition, if you don't want to use the docker image as above, you can "
"also build all from source:"
msgstr "此外，如果您不想使用上述 Docker 镜像，也可以从源码构建所有组件："

msgid ""
"- Install `vllm-ascend` from source, refer to "
"[installation](../../installation.md)."
msgstr "- 从源码安装 `vllm-ascend`，请参考[安装指南](../../installation.md)。"

msgid ""
"If you want to deploy multi-node environment, you need to set up environment"
" on each node."
msgstr "如需部署多节点环境，需要在每个节点上进行环境设置。"

msgid "## Deployment"
msgstr "## 部署"

msgid ""
"In this tutorial, we suppose you downloaded the model weight to "
"`/root/.cache/`. Feel free to change it to your own path."
msgstr "在本教程中，我们假设您已将模型权重下载到 `/root/.cache/`。您可以根据需要更改为自己的路径。"

msgid "### Single-node Deployment"
msgstr "### 单节点部署"

msgid ""
"- Quantized model `DeepSeek-V3.2-w8a8` can be deployed on 1 Atlas 800 A3 "
"(64G × 16)."
msgstr "- 量化模型 `DeepSeek-V3.2-w8a8` 可部署在 1 个 Atlas 800 A3（64G × 16）上。"

msgid "Run the following script to execute online inference."
msgstr "运行以下脚本执行在线推理。"

msgid "### Multi-node Deployment"
msgstr "### 多节点部署"

msgid "- `DeepSeek-V3.2-w8a8`: require at least 2 Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 8)."
msgstr "- `DeepSeek-V3.2-w8a8`：至少需要 2 个 Atlas 800 A2（64G × 8）。"

msgid "Run the following scripts on two nodes respectively."
msgstr "分别在两个节点上运行以下脚本。"

msgid "### Prefill-Decode Disaggregation"
msgstr "### 预填充-解码分离"

msgid ""
"We'd like to show the deployment guide of `DeepSeek-V3.2` on multi-node "
"environment with 1P1D for better performance."
msgstr "我们将展示 `DeepSeek-V3.2` 在多节点环境下采用 1P1D 配置以获得更好性能的部署指南。"

msgid "Before you start, please"
msgstr "开始之前，请"

msgid "1. prepare the script `launch_online_dp.py` on each node:"
msgstr "1. 在每个节点上准备脚本 `launch_online_dp.py`："

msgid "2. prepare the script `run_dp_template.sh` on each node."
msgstr "2. 在每个节点上准备脚本 `run_dp_template.sh`。"

msgid ""
"Once the preparation is done, you can start the server with the following command on each node:\n"
"Refer to [Distributed DP Server With Large-Scale Expert Parallelism](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/user_guide/feature_guide/large_scale_ep.html) to get the detailed boot method."
msgstr ""
"准备工作完成后，您可以在每个节点上使用以下命令启动服务器：\n"
"请参考[大规模专家并行分布式 DP 服务器](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/user_guide/feature_guide/large_scale_ep.html)获取详细的启动方法。"

msgid "1. Prefill node 0"
msgstr "1. 预填充节点 0"

msgid "2. Prefill node 1"
msgstr "2. 预填充节点 1"

msgid "3. Decode node 0"
msgstr "3. 解码节点 0"

msgid "4. Decode node 1"
msgstr "4. 解码节点 1"

msgid "### Request Forwarding"
msgstr "### 请求转发"

msgid ""
"To set up request forwarding, run the following script on any machine. You "
"can get the proxy program in the repository's examples: "
"[load_balance_proxy_layerwise_server_example.py](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/main/examples/disaggregated_prefill_v1/load_balance_proxy_layerwise_server_example.py)"
msgstr ""
"要设置请求转发，请在任意机器上运行以下脚本。您可以在仓库的示例中找到代理程序：[load_balance_proxy_layerwise_server_example.py](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/main/examples/disaggregated_prefill_v1/load_balance_proxy_layerwise_server_example.py)"

msgid "## Functional Verification"
msgstr "## 功能验证"

msgid ""
"Once your server is started, you can query the model with input prompts:"
msgstr "服务器启动后，您可以使用输入提示词查询模型："

msgid "**Note**:"
msgstr "**注意**："

msgid ""
"- `<node0_ip>`: The IP address of the node where the server is running (e.g., localhost). For PD-separated deployment, use the host IP of the node where the proxy script resides.\n"
"- `<port>`: The port number specified in the server startup command (e.g., 8000). For PD-separated deployment, use the port configured in the proxy script."
msgstr ""
"- `<node0_ip>`：运行服务器的节点 IP 地址（例如 localhost）。对于 PD 分离部署，请使用代理脚本所在节点的主机 IP。\n"
"- `<port>`：服务器启动命令中指定的端口号（例如 8000）。对于 PD 分离部署，请使用代理脚本中配置的端口。"

msgid "**Expected Result**:"
msgstr "**预期结果**："

msgid "## Accuracy Evaluation"
msgstr "## 精度评估"

msgid "Here are two accuracy evaluation methods."
msgstr "这里提供两种精度评估方法。"

msgid ""
"1. Refer to [Using "
"AISBench](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_ais_bench.md) for details."
msgstr ""
"1. 详细信息请参考[使用 "
"AISBench](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_ais_bench.md)。"

msgid "2. After execution, you can get the result."
msgstr "2. 执行后即可获取结果。"

msgid "### Using Language Model Evaluation Harness"
msgstr "### 使用 Language Model Evaluation Harness"

msgid ""
"As an example, take the `gsm8k` dataset as a test dataset, and run accuracy "
"evaluation of `DeepSeek-V3.2-W8A8` in online mode."
msgstr "以 `gsm8k` 数据集作为测试数据集为例，在线模式下运行 `DeepSeek-V3.2-W8A8` 的精度评估。"

msgid ""
"1. Refer to [Using "
"lm_eval](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_lm_eval.md) for `lm_eval` "
"installation."
msgstr ""
"1. 请参考[使用 lm_eval](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_lm_eval.md) 安装 "
"`lm_eval`。"

msgid "2. Run `lm_eval` to execute the accuracy evaluation."
msgstr "2. 运行 `lm_eval` 执行精度评估。"

msgid "3. After execution, you can get the result."
msgstr "3. 执行后即可获取结果。"

msgid "## Performance"
msgstr "## 性能"

msgid ""
"Refer to [Using AISBench for performance "
"evaluation](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_ais_bench.md#execute-"
"performance-evaluation) for details."
msgstr ""
"详情请参考[使用AISBench进行性能评估](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_ais_bench.md#execute-"
"performance-evaluation)。"

msgid "The performance result is:"
msgstr "性能结果如下："

msgid "**Hardware**: A3-752T, 4 node"
msgstr "**硬件**：A3-752T，4节点"

msgid "**Deployment**: 1P1D, Prefill node: DP2+TP16, Decode Node: DP8+TP4"
msgstr "**部署**：1P1D，Prefill节点：DP2+TP16，Decode节点：DP8+TP4"

msgid "**Input/Output**: 64k/3k"
msgstr "**输入/输出**：64k/3k"

msgid "**Performance**: 533tps, TPOT 32ms"
msgstr "**性能**：533tps，TPOT 32ms"

msgid "### Using vLLM Benchmark"
msgstr "### 使用vLLM基准测试"

msgid "Run performance evaluation of `DeepSeek-V3.2-W8A8` as an example."
msgstr "以`DeepSeek-V3.2-W8A8`为例进行性能评估。"

msgid ""
"Refer to [vllm benchmark](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/benchmarking/) for "
"more details."
msgstr "更多详情请参考[vllm基准测试](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/benchmarking/)。"

msgid "There are three `vllm bench` subcommands:"
msgstr "`vllm bench`包含三个子命令："

msgid ""
"- `latency`: Benchmark the latency of a single batch of requests.\n"
"- `serve`: Benchmark the online serving throughput.\n"
"- `throughput`: Benchmark offline inference throughput."
msgstr ""
"- `latency`：对单批请求的延迟进行基准测试。\n"
"- `serve`：对在线服务吞吐量进行基准测试。\n"
"- `throughput`：对离线推理吞吐量进行基准测试。"

msgid "Take the `serve` as an example. Run the code as follows."
msgstr "以`serve`为例，运行代码如下。"

msgid "## Function Call"
msgstr "## 函数调用"

msgid ""
"The function call feature is supported from v0.13.0rc1 on. Please use the "
"latest version."
msgstr "函数调用功能从v0.13.0rc1版本开始支持，请使用最新版本。"

msgid ""
"Refer to [DeepSeek-V3.2 Usage "
"Guide](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/recipes/en/latest/DeepSeek/DeepSeek-V3_2.html#tool-"
"calling-example) for details."
msgstr ""
"详情请参考[DeepSeek-V3.2使用指南](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/recipes/en/latest/DeepSeek/DeepSeek-V3_2.html#tool-"
"calling-example)。"

msgid "Start the docker image on your each node."
msgstr "在每个节点上启动 Docker 镜像。"

